title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Afters with Himanshu Suri
description:
The Afters with Himanshu “Heems” Suri

On our new weekly lightning round mini ep with Himanshu “Heems” Suri, we’re fucking around with the Grammys, Stoffa, reliving your golden years, erasing Das Racist from history, Nav’s barber, Danny Brown’s orthodontist, being a known racist, only eating Pizza Hut and Taco Bell, collabing with Rammstein vs. Insane Clown Posse, white people, Ezra Koening, Indian food and much more.

For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
